title: Interactive Shiny Dashboard TishLL
text:
This dashboard provides interactive visualizations for our data analysis project.
Unfortunately, publishing is deprecated on Posit Cloud, and the process to sunset this feature began at the end of December, 2024, this content is no longer accessible. So that’s as far as I can go with this project unfortunately.

title: Interactive Shiny Dashboard TishLL
text:
About This Dashboard
This dashboard was created using R Shiny and showcases various aspects of the data analysis, including:

Data visualization
Statistical summaries
Interactive plots

Feel free to explore the different features and interact with the visualizations to gain insights into the dataset.

title: Interactive Shiny Dashboard TishLL
text:
How to Use

Use the navigation menu to switch between different views.
Interact with the plots and tables by clicking, hovering, or selecting options.
Adjust any available parameters to customize the visualizations.
